WEBVTT

00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:02.440
Razmišljala sam.

00:00:04.240 --> 00:00:06.000
Ubiću svog tatu.

00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:08.416
Pozvala sam sestru.

00:00:08.440 --> 00:00:09.936
„Slušaj.

00:00:09.960 --> 00:00:11.520
Razmišljala sam.

00:00:12.480 --> 00:00:14.320
Ubiću tatu.

00:00:15.480 --> 00:00:17.120
Odvešću ga u Oregon,

00:00:18.080 --> 00:00:19.976
naći ću heroin

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:21.240
i daću mu ga.“

00:00:22.720 --> 00:00:24.856
Moj tata ima frontotemporalnu demenciju,

00:00:24.880 --> 00:00:26.480
ili FTD.

00:00:26.510 --> 00:00:29.756
To je zbunjujuća bolest koja pogađa ljude
u 50-im ili 60-im godinama.

00:00:29.776 --> 00:00:32.496
Može u potpunosti promeniti ličnost osobe,